===Etymology 1===
{{ja-kanjitab|あ|sort=あく|yomi=kun}}

====Verb====
{{ja-verb|type=1|tr=intrans|あく}}

# to [[open]]
#: {{ja-usex|彼女のシャツに小さな穴が'''開いています'''。|かのじょ の シャツ に ちいさな あな が '''あいています'''。|There is a small hole on her shirt. (lit. ''A small hole is '''opening''' on her shirt.'')}}
# to [[begin]] {{rfex|ja}}

=====Usage notes=====
The passive, causative, and volitional of あく are never used.

